      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，网段没错。子网就写web/app/db/mgmt四个，用斜杠隔开就行，不用展开太多细节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "VNet: 10.10.0.0/16",
        "Subnets: web/app/db/mgmt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我把Azure订阅做成一个子图，里面放资源组、VNet和子网。本地环境我标注成On-Prem，里面包含VyOS路由器和虚拟机，这样可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "RG",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets",
        "On-Prem (VyOS + VMs)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以，这样层次很清楚。对了，流量方向要体现出来——互联网到VNet是单向的，本地到VNet是双向的，这个很重要。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Internet",
        "VNet",
        "On-Prem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "我先画一版出来。Azure订阅作为子图，里面资源组用圆角括号表示，VNet和子网放下面。然后互联网和本地环境放在子图外面，用箭头连起来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Azure Subscription",
        "RG",
        "VNet",
        "Subnets",
        "Internet",
        "On-Prem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
