      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，这样格式就对了。子图的标题用\"Azure Subscription\"，本地环境标注\"On-Prem (VyOS + VMs)\"，这些文字都准确。",
      "elements_involved": [
